Class JobDetailFactoryBean

Simplified version of Spring's MethodInvokingJobDetailFactoryBean that avoids issues with non-serializable classes (for JDBC storage).

author:
Burt Beckwith
author:

setJobListenerNames

public void setJobListenerNames(def names)
Set a list of JobListener names for this job, referring to non-global JobListeners registered with the Scheduler.

A JobListener name always refers to the name returned by the JobListener implementation.

param:
names array of job listener names which should be applied to the job
see:
SchedulerFactoryBean#setJobListeners
see:
org.quartz.JobListener#getName
